
Ranger Help for: heartshot
==========================

SYNTAX:      heartshot <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   14
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  bow

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger a special attack with crossbows. The Ranger
takes an extra carefully aimed shot for the target's heart. The Ranger
must be wielding a crossbow and carrying at least one bolt.

Heartshot uses the best bolt available and is intended as a finishing
shot. It deals heavy single-target damage based on dexterity, Ranger
progression, crossbow quality, and bolt quality. A poor shot still clips
the target for partial damage, while a clean hit is much stronger.
Wounded targets are especially vulnerable.
